collection: publications
permalink: /publication/2009-10-01-paper-title-number-2
excerpt: 'Our aim is to conduct research in ways that are respectful to deaf participants. In the development of a demographic questionnaire in ASL, we encountered
several challenges in both technical and linguistic-cultural areas that needed to be overcome. Our experience is shared in this paper'
